			<div class="post-609 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-civil-unrest category-constitution category-gold-price-suppression-scheme tag-abraham-lincoln tag-civil-unrest tag-constitution tag-federal-reserve tag-franklin-roosevelt tag-gold-confiscation tag-hydra post_box top" id="post-609">
